Ok, I was wrong I do have more to say (don't I always?)<P>While I like the idea of having this spell, it is another example of the distinction between classes fading out, similar in many ways to making unlimited sow available to everyone with 5kpp.  It seems like a good thing on the surface, but is a bad thing.  <P>I like having different classes, with different capabilities.  Sure it would be nice to have the abilities of all the classes rolled into one... but it would be bad for the game, and not much fun once the novelty wore off.<P>Slurm!<P>--------------------<P>Slurm Fearbringer<BR>51st Iksar Shaman -E'ci<BR>Pillars of Heaven -officer
